DiatomsATTACK.bio: I am a paleoecologist specializing in microscopic algae known as diatoms. Diatoms have an opaline cell wall that readily fossilizes, allowing me to explore their occurrences over very long time scales. I like making tiny, intricate organisms visible and enjoyable to everyone.
